# How to?
# 1. Install the REST Client extension: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client
# 2. Add your requests. Example:

### Global: title, logo and social media

GET http://localhost:1337/api/global?fields[0]=title&populate[logo][fields][0]=url&populate[socialMedia]=*
Authorization: Bearer 046044b3e618b298f9106c85e771160ddd611329be2978cf933d6eeaf0130657c2b8cd2a528fee2bdb8d7eac30e4c62f70f133db41e18382ab8f2b40332f6ef2a340c27822a3250702c10ca3af2adae131b36424795b43361034d64b54115667d40fc346dea0de269314a70ab69671ff89d1915a4633560225e882490134a74e

### Store items: id, title, description, cover {url}, isActive, category and prices {price, currency, isActive}

